trans-unit.source: Narrow down the list of maintenance order operations based on their work center. The input help shows all work centers that are currently assigned to you.

The input help shows all work centers that are currently assigned to you.

target.mrk: 워크 센터별로 유지보수 오더 작업 리스트의 범위를 좁힙니다.
입력 도움말에 현재 사용자에게 지정된 워크 센터가 모두 표시됩니다.

trans-unit.source: Using this filter has the following effect:

seg-source.mrk: Using this filter has the following effect:

trans-unit.source: The <uicontrol>Maintenance Order Operations</uicontrol> tab shows operations and suboperations for the relevant work centers.

seg-source.mrk: The <uicontrol>Maintenance Order Operations</uicontrol> tab shows operations and suboperations for the relevant work centers.

target.mrk: <uicontrol>유지보수 오더 작업</uicontrol> 탭에 관련 워크 센터의 작업과 하위 작업이 표시됩니다.

trans-unit.source: The <uicontrol>Maintenance Orders</uicontrol> tab shows the orders that include the filtered operations, even if the main work center is a different one.

seg-source.mrk: The <uicontrol>Maintenance Orders</uicontrol> tab shows the orders that include the filtered operations, even if the main work center is a different one.

target.mrk: <uicontrol>유지보수 오더</uicontrol> 탭에 필터링된 작업에 포함된 오더가 표시됩니다(주요 워크 센터가 다른 경우도 포함).
